Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BRAND NEW WAREHOUSE – READY FOR OCCUPATION

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present for your consideration Steel Street, Narangba. Brought to the market by CBRE this estate has the capability for Design & Construct, land sales and lease opportunities.

Steel Street, Narangba situated approximately 26 radial kilometres north of the Brisbane CBD. 

• Adjacent to Boundary Road upgrade interchange 
• Excellent access to Bruce Highway via Boundary Road
• Recent commitments to the area include Caltex, Grand Prix Mazda, Hitec Glazing, Nick Scali, Marinucci Packaging and Costco.

Lot 3 Steel Street SPEC BUILD will be kicking off in the new year 

•	Total GFA 1,171sqm x 2 units 
•	Warehouse GFA 943sqm
•	Office/Showroom GFA 228sqm
•	Internal Clearance 8.2 metres minimum clearance
•	Car Parks 8 car parks
•	Container Set Down Provisions 20ft & 40ft

Estate Features include:

•	Level on-grade lots sizing from 4,000sqm to 20,000sqm (approx.)
•	Serviced, compacted, zoned lots ready to build on
•	General Industry capabilities subject to council approval

For more information please contact Exclusive Agents Dillon Murphy & Hugh Adnam of CBRE.
